WiFi & BT Module
----------------

|Product| is equipped with the popular **Realtek RTL8723 WiFi/BT module** that supports BT/BLE 4.0 (with backward compatibility), as well as 802.11bgn 2.4 GHz Wireless LAN (WLAN). 

.. figure:: /Media/Pi/A53/Others/WiFi_BT.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *RTL8273 WiFi/BT Module*

The enclosed (|productP|) variant of the product also includes an SMA connector for an external WiFi/BT antenna, as illustrated in the figure below.

.. figure:: /Media/Pi/A53/Others/Antenna.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *WiFi+BT Antenna*

:pagebreak:`True`
